&lt;li&gt;镜像列表: &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.debian.org/mirror/list&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;external&quot;&gt;http://www.debian.org/mirror/list&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
